ánh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/Ho%E1%BA%A1-Qu%E1%BA%A3ng-Tr%E1%BB%8B-ni%E1%BA%BFt-s%E1%BB%A9-H%E1%BB%93-H%E1%BB%AFu-Nguy%C3%AAn-thu-d%E1%BA%A1-phi%E1%BA%BFm-du-H%C3%A3n-giang-nguy%C3%AAn-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-9PECkGE_ZlaP8CgIDSHY3g">Hoạ Quảng Trị niết sứ Hồ Hữu Nguyên thu dạ phiếm du Hãn giang nguyên vận - 和廣治臬使胡友元秋夜泛遊捍江原韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/author-eQ6wft6d1E9_uEITUaRRlg">Nguyễn Phúc Ưng Bình</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/L%E1%BA%A1c-nh%E1%BA%ADt/poem-pOGicUXiKDHbDJr4DMqV-g">Lạc nhật - 落日</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ch%C3%A2u-H%E1%BA%A3i-%C4%90%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng/L%C3%A3ng-%C4%91%C3%A0o-sa-Giang-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-%E1%BA%A9m-th%E1%BB%A9-T%E1%BA%A3i-Chi-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-4xcqzbROOYbcJbTgjIVu4g">Lãng đào sa - Giang thượng ẩm, thứ Tải Chi vận - 浪淘沙－江上飲，次載之韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ch%C3%A2u-H%E1%BA%A3i-%C4%90%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng/author-ioE9gUDRRK0CF1f-0I-Dgw">Châu Hải Đường</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Xu%C3%A2n-%C3%94n/T%E1%BB%ADu-h%E1%BB%A9ng/poem-eHUzbxzD-hnroba6fX3SSw">Tửu hứng - 酒興</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Xu%C3%A2n-%C3%94n/author-MvAX8pIr0uu6mqdrhe1jhA">Nguyễn Xuân Ôn</a>)<br></div>	</div>
